{
  "title": "Mildly Briny Dutch Carnaroli Rice Pilaf",
  "description": "A comforting Dutch dish featuring Carnaroli rice, with a mother sauce base and a mildly briny flavor, this pilaf is a perfect side dish for any meal, and is shojin-friendly.",
